  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "\tYou are the manager of an ecological cafe. Your goal is to maximize
    income while minimizing environmental pollution. Customers buy food at the checkout,
    but they also tend to drop litter on the way back, which pollutes the environment
    and eventually leads to ecological disaster. Your second source of income is
    a growing area periodically providing crates of raw food that can be sold at
    the kitchen. However, nothing can grow if the pollution level is too high. To
    improve the ecological situation you have to build improvements such as waste
    bins and refinery, and also get rid of waste in time."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: e66bb29cbbca3674fb7f486af37aee9f, type: 2}
